---
import ButtonLiveProduction from "../../components/ButtonLiveProduction/ButtonLiveProduction.astro";
import NatanyaIcon from "./Natanya/NatanyaIcon.astro";
import ProjectSlider from "./ProjectSlider.astro";
---

<article class="max-w-[1244px] mx-auto z-10 relative py-20 sm:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Outnament Lines (Top) -->
  <img
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines.png"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    loading="lazy"
    alt=""
    class="absolute pointer-events-none z-0 left-0 top-0 min-w-[600px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <!-- Outnament Lines (Bottom) -->
  <img
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines-btm.png"
    loading="lazy"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    alt=""
    class="absolute pointer-events-none z-0 right-0 bottom-0 min-w-[500px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <div class="lg:px-16 sm:px-10 px-5 relative z-10">
    <h3 class="sr-only">Natanya</h3>
    <NatanyaIcon />

    <h4 class="sr-only">About Natanya</h4>

    <p class="sm:text-2xl text-xl !leading-150 text-dark mt-10">
      <span class="font-semibold">Introducing Natanya</span> - an interactive polling tool that makes it easy to create engaging
      polls and collect data from an audience in real-time. It can be used during live events, and the results can be displayed
      with a chart data visualization.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-images py-10 sm:py-20">
    <ProjectSlider />
  </div>

  <div class="lg:px-16 sm:px-10 px-5 relative z-10">
    <p class="sm:text-2xl text-xl !leading-150 text-dark">
      Maybe you're ever heard about Slido? Mentimeter? Yes, Natanya is the alternative of those services. The
      difference? It is free ü§ë and open source.
      <br />
      <br />
      Why create this project? My team (core web experience) at GovTech wanted to find an ‚Äúeconomical way‚Äù to host a survey
      during a live event, similar to using Slido.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-[4.4rem] mb-10 sm:mb-14">
      <ButtonLiveProduction />
    </div>

    <div class="pl-5 sm:pl-8 flex items-start space-x-4 sm:space-x-10">
      <a href="#" class="tracking-tight font-semibold leading-6">
        <span class="block text-xl sm:text-[32px] text-dark leading-4 sm:!leading-100">natanya</span>
        <span class="inline-flex text-sm sm:text-xl space-x-[6px] text-slate-700 sm:pt-2">
          <span>a</span>
          <span
            ><svg class="w-[18px] sm:w-6 sm:h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <g clip-path="url(#clip0_67_250)">
                <path
                  d="M12.5 0.297119C5.87 0.297119 0.5 5.67012 0.5 12.2971C0.5 17.6001 3.938 22.0971 8.705 23.6821C9.305 23.7951 9.525 23.4241 9.525 23.1051C9.525 22.8201 9.515 22.0651 9.51 21.0651C6.172 21.7891 5.468 19.4551 5.468 19.4551C4.922 18.0701 4.133 17.7001 4.133 17.7001C3.046 16.9561 4.217 16.9711 4.217 16.9711C5.422 17.0551 6.055 18.2071 6.055 18.2071C7.125 20.0421 8.864 19.5121 9.55 19.2051C9.658 18.4291 9.967 17.9001 10.31 17.6001C7.645 17.3001 4.844 16.2681 4.844 11.6701C4.844 10.3601 5.309 9.29012 6.079 8.45012C5.944 8.14712 5.539 6.92712 6.184 5.27412C6.184 5.27412 7.189 4.95212 9.484 6.50412C10.444 6.23712 11.464 6.10512 12.484 6.09912C13.504 6.10512 14.524 6.23712 15.484 6.50412C17.764 4.95212 18.769 5.27412 18.769 5.27412C19.414 6.92712 19.009 8.14712 18.889 8.45012C19.654 9.29012 20.119 10.3601 20.119 11.6701C20.119 16.2801 17.314 17.2951 14.644 17.5901C15.064 17.9501 15.454 18.6861 15.454 19.8101C15.454 21.4161 15.439 22.7061 15.439 23.0961C15.439 23.4111 15.649 23.7861 16.264 23.6661C21.065 22.0921 24.5 17.5921 24.5 12.2971C24.5 5.67012 19.127 0.297119 12.5 0.297119"
